---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <article class="mb-20 px-12 md:px-20 lg:px-64">
    <header class="py-6 pt-8">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-1">
        <!-- small arrow icon -->
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="h-6 w-6"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            stroke-width="2"
            d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
        </svg>
        <span>Home</span>
      </a>
    </header>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>
      This privacy policy outlines how <strong>Clean YouTube</strong> handles user
      information. We are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring transparency.
      This extension does not collect, store, or share any personal information from
      its users.
    </p>

    <h2>No Personal Data Collected</h2>
    <p>
      We do not collect any personal data or information from users. Our
      extension functions without the need to gather, store, or process any
      personal or identifiable information.
    </p>

    <h2>Usage of Our Extension</h2>
    <p>
      Our extension operates solely on your local device and does not transmit
      any data to external servers. All functionalities provided by the
      extension are executed locally on your browser.
    </p>

    <h2>User Rights</h2>
    <p>
      Since we do not collect any personal data, there are no data-related
      rights applicable to our users. If you have any questions or concerns
      about our privacy practices, please contact us at <a
        href="mailto:[your-email@example.com]">[your-email@example.com]</a
      >.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>
      We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be
      posted on this page, and if we decide to collect personal data in the
      future, we will inform users and update this policy accordingly.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please
      contact us at <a href="mailto:jeegs.creator@gmail.com" class="underline"
        >jeegs.creator@gmail.com</a
      >.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  p {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: #ccc;
  }
</style>
